{
  "chapter": 2,
  "chapter_summary": "陆小凤因怕晕船选择了一条大海船，却遇到狡猾的船主人老狐狸。在等待装货期间，陆小凤来到老狐狸开设的狐狸窝消遣。他遇到一个只吃煮鸡蛋的冷漠少年岳洋，对其产生好奇。岳洋多次遭遇暗杀，陆小凤出手相助却遭冷遇。岳洋的大哥胡生出现，两人关系复杂。原来岳洋是被训练的杀手，接到命令要杀死胡生，但最终发现这只是考验。陆小凤发现独眼老渔人企图用毒水害岳洋，出手阻止。最后老渔人离奇淹死，船终于要开了。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "speaker_name": "老狐狸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "货装得越多，船走起来越稳，就算你没有出过海，也绝不会晕船的，反正你又不急，多等两天有什么关系？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "speaker_name": "老狐狸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我还可以介绍个好地方给你，到了那里，说不定你就不想走了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那地方有什么？",
      "tone": "陆小凤忍不住",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "speaker_name": "老狐狸",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "只要你能想得出来的，那地方都有。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "text": "那地方是不是你开的？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "speaker_name": "老狐狸",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你是个聪明人，所以我第一眼看见你，就已开始喜欢你。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "这里难得有牛肉，你吃一点。",
      "tone": "轻轻地",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "这是我送给你的，不用钱，你不吃也不行。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刚才那个小姑娘是谁？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "女人",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这里的小姑娘有好几十个，我怎么知道你说的是哪一个？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就是脸上有牛肉汤的那个。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那个只吃煮鸡蛋的小伙子是谁？姓什么？叫什么？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只希望他被鸡蛋活活噎死。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "他回房睡觉去了，每天他都睡得很早。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你想不想吃牛肉？",
      "tone": "忽然轻轻地",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "我也想睡觉去。",
      "tone": "轻轻地",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我外婆常说，要得到一个男人的心，最快的一条路就是先打通他的肠胃。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "可是你们两个为什么对吃连一点兴趣都没有？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "因为我怕发胖。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "我们不进去？",
      "tone": "陆小凤忍不住",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "现在里面还有人，还得等一下。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不过这些男人都像饿狗一样，用不了两下就会出来的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ji",
      "speaker_name": "小鸡",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你嘴上的这两条东西，究竟是眉毛？还是胡子？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "你究竟做了些什么事？是抢了人家的饭碗？还是偷了人家的老婆？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "别人想要你的命，你一点都不在乎？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "你也不想知道暗算你的人是谁？",
      "tone": "陆小凤",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我只在乎一件事。",
      "tone": "岳洋忽然",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "陆小凤",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "若有人总喜欢管我的闲事，我就会很想让他以后永远管不了别人的闲事。",
      "tone": "岳洋",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "幸好他也有二十左右了，否则别人岂非要把他当做我的儿子？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来两个人都是死人。",
      "tone": "恨恨地",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我实在不明白你究竟是怎么样的一个人，三更半夜的，为什么还不睡觉？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "因为我吃错了药。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你吃错了什么药？春药？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "就算你吃了春药，也该来找我的，为什么去找男人？你是不是有什么毛病？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "我的毛病还不止一种。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你还有什么病？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "饿病！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这种病倒没关系。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我刚好有种专治这种病的药。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "牛肉？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "馒头夹牛肉，再用一大壶吊在海水里冻得冰凉的糯米酒送下去，你看怎么样？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "我看天下再也找不出比这种更好的药了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "那个人是你朋友？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "他不是我朋友。",
      "tone": "岳洋",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "他是我大哥。",
      "tone": "岳洋",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你也要出海去？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你也准备坐老狐狸那条船？",
      "tone": "岳洋",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你最好换一条船。",
      "tone": "冷冷",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陆小凤",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为我付了五百两银子，把那条船包下来了。",
      "tone": "岳洋",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "我也很想换条船，只可惜我也付了五百两银子把那条船包下了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "speaker_name": "老狐狸",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "那是条大船，多坐一个人也不会沉的，你们两位又都急着要出海。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "speaker_name": "老狐狸",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "船上的人越多越热闹，何况，能同船共渡，也是五百年修来的，你若想换条船，我也可以把船钱退给你，可是最多只能退四百两。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "speaker_name": "老狐狸",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "怎么样？",
      "tone": "笑嘻嘻的",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "text": "不怎么样。",
      "tone": "叹着气",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "speaker_name": "老狐狸",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我看你一定是牛肉汤喝得太多了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这是五百两银子，就算我赔你的船钱，你一定要换条船。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "你是不是一定要坐老狐狸那条船？却一定不让我坐？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "岳洋",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陆小凤",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为我不喜欢多管闲事的人。",
      "tone": "岳洋",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你不肯？",
      "tone": "岳洋变色",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "是的！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "岳洋",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "因为那是条大船，多坐一个人也不会沉下去！",
      "tone": "忽然",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你不后悔？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "我这一辈子从来也没有后悔过一次。",
      "tone": "陆小凤淡淡",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "speaker_name": "老狐狸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "货已装好，明天一早就开船。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "胡生",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "你睡得好不好？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_hu_sheng",
      "text": "不好，我睡不着。",
      "tone": "岳洋",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "胡生",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "那个长着四条眉毛的人还有没有来找你麻烦？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_hu_sheng",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "岳洋",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "胡生",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "其实你根本就不必担心他，他根本就是个无足轻重的人。",
      "tone": "胡生",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_hu_sheng",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "岳洋",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "胡生",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "这是你上船之前的最后一次指示，做完之后，就可以上船了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "胡生",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "指示中要你做什么事？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "胡生",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "这次是要你做什么？",
      "tone": "胡生又在",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_hu_sheng",
      "text": "要我杀了你。",
      "tone": "才一字字",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "胡生",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "你能有今天，是谁造成的？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_hu_sheng",
      "text": "是你！",
      "tone": "岳洋",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "胡生",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "但你却要杀我！",
      "tone": "胡生",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_hu_sheng",
      "text": "我并不想杀你，可是我非杀不可！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "胡生",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "反正也没有人知道的，你难道就不能抗命一次？",
      "tone": "胡生",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_hu_sheng",
      "text": "我不能。",
      "tone": "岳洋",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "胡生",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "那么你就不该告诉我。",
      "tone": "缓缓",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_hu_sheng",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "岳洋",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "胡生",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "你若是乘机暗算，也许还能得手，现在我既然已知道，死的就是你。",
      "tone": "胡生冷冷",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "胡生",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "等一等，你再看看我身上的另一指示！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "胡生",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "这不过是试探你的，看你是不是能绝对遵守命令。",
      "tone": "喘息着",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "胡生",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "现在你已通过了这一关，已完全合格。快上船去吧。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "这个人已经是你的了！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我要这么样一个人干什么？",
      "tone": "冷冷",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "你难道不想问是谁想害你？",
      "tone": "陆小凤",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我用不着问，我知道是谁想害我！",
      "tone": "岳洋",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "是谁？",
      "tone": "陆小凤",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 582
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你！",
      "tone": "岳洋",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我想喝水，你却打落我的水壶，不是你害我，是谁害我？",
      "tone": "岳洋冷冷",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 588
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_lao_yu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独眼老渔人",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你不但害了他，也害了我，我这条膀子已经快被你捏断了，我得要你赔。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 590
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_du_yan_lao_yu_ren",
      "text": "赔，我赔，这锭银子就算我给你喝酒的！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 592
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你能不能帮我一个忙？",
      "tone": "忽然",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 596
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "你说。",
      "tone": "陆小凤",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 598
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "离我远一点，越远越好。",
      "tone": "岳洋",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 600
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_shou",
      "speaker_name": "水手",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "开船了，开船了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_num": 622
    }
